      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six. This unit exhibits strong compression across all cylinders and a recently serviced VANOS system for optimal cam timing. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission shifts with precision, paired with a reinforced rear subframe to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. Equipped with the factory M Variable Differential Lock, the power delivery remains predictable through every apex. The suspension maintains its factory geometry with refreshed bushings, offering the communicative feedback and tactile steering response synonymous with this chassis. A driver-focused example that balances raw performance with mechanical longevity.",
