      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine, equipped with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing for a linear power band up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis has been maintained with an emphasis on longevity, including reinforced subframe mounting points and refreshed suspension bushings to ensure structural rigidity. While showing minor cosmetic wear consistent with its age, the mechanical vitals are strong, benefiting from a recent valve adjustment and a cooling system overhaul. It maintains a planted stance on staggered Style 67 wheels, offering the communicative steering and balanced turn-in characteristic of this legendary platform.",
